OL,3,CSouth Shields Customs House marks the
OL,4,Cend of an era as Ray Spencer steps down
OL,6,FKatie Cole sat down with Ray Spencer
OL,7,Fas he looked back on 25 years at the
OL,8,Fhead of The Customs House.
OL,10,FHundreds of people have celebrated the
OL,11,Fman behind one of most well-known
OL,12,Finstitutions as he steps down from his
OL,13,Frole for a final time.
OL,15,FRay Spencer MBE has been executive
OL,16,Fdirector of the Customs House in for
OL,17,Fthe past 25 years but is now passing
OL,18,Fthe baton on.
