OL,3,CSouth Shields Customs House marks the
OL,4,Cend of an era as Ray Spencer steps down
OL,6,FIn honour of him, the Customs House
OL,7,Fmain auditorium has been renamed 'The
OL,8,FRay Spencer Theatre.'
OL,10,FIn the newly named theatre, he said an
OL,11,Femotional goodbye ahead of officially
OL,12,Fstepping down on Thursday 28 March.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV Tyne Tees, Mr Spencer
OL,15,Fsaid: "I'm 67, I think it's time to
OL,16,Fmake room for other people. There's a
OL,17,Flot of talent around and perhaps it's
OL,18,Ftheir opportunity to steer the ship.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
