OL,3,CSouth Shields Customs House marks the
OL,4,Cend of an era as Ray Spencer steps down
OL,6,F"Also, when you run an organisation
OL,7,Fyou can't always do the things that
OL,8,Fyou want to do, you've got to do
OL,9,Fthings that you have to do. Now I'll
OL,10,Fdo something I want to do, so perhaps
OL,11,FI'll act a bit, travel a bit and have
OL,12,Ffun."
OL,14,FOver the years, Mr Spencer has played
OL,15,Fan important role on stage in addition
OL,16,Fto his job behind the scenes. When he
OL,17,Ffirst took charge he was Tommy the
OL,18,FTrumpeter - a crowd favourite in South
OL,19,FShields.
