OL,3,CSouth Shields Customs House marks the
OL,4,Cend of an era as Ray Spencer steps down
OL,6,FThese days he's better known as Dame
OL,7,FBella in the venue's annual pantomime.
OL,8,FHe will continue to write, direct and
OL,9,Fstar in the annual pantomime, playing
OL,10,Fthe popular character Dame Bella.
OL,12,FHe said: "As long as the legs still
OL,13,Fwork and people aren't carrying me,
OL,14,FI'll still want to write, direct and
OL,15,Fbe in the pantomime because I
OL,16,Fabsolutely love it."
