OL,3,CSouth Shields Customs House marks the
OL,4,Cend of an era as Ray Spencer steps down
OL,6,FDuring his tenure as head of the South
OL,7,FTyneside institution, Mr Spencer has
OL,8,Fsupported a wealth of local talent,
OL,9,Fhelping to inspire and launch the
OL,10,Fcareers of many.
OL,12,FMr Spencer joined the Customs House
OL,13,Fwhen the theatre and arts complex was
OL,14,Fon the verge of bankruptcy.
OL,16,FSince then he has transformed the
OL,17,Fvenue making it one of the region's
OL,18,Fleading arts and entertainment venues.
