OL,3,CSouth Shields Customs House marks the
OL,4,Cend of an era as Ray Spencer steps down
OL,6,FOver the years he has been given
OL,7,Fseveral honours to recognise his
OL,8,Fdedication. In 2010 he became an MBE,
OL,9,Freceiving his award from Queen
OL,10,FElizabeth II for his services to the
OL,11,Farts. Two years later he was given an
OL,12,FHonorary Arts Fellowship from
OL,13,FSunderland University.
