OL,3,CSouth Shields Customs House marks the
OL,4,Cend of an era as Ray Spencer steps down
OL,6,FIn 2022 the Customs House Director was
OL,7,Fbestowed the Freedom of South Tyneside
OL,8,Fwhich was in recognition of his
OL,9,Fservice and contribution to the
OL,10,Fcultural and civic life of South
OL,11,FTyneside. At the time he was only one
OL,12,Fof ten other people or organisations
OL,13,Fto have been awarded the honour since
OL,14,F1981.
OL,16,FAmong those who turned out to
OL,17,Fcelebrate the South Shields icon was
OL,18,Flocal singer Joe McElderry.
