OL,3,CSouth Shields Customs House marks the
OL,4,Cend of an era as Ray Spencer steps down
OL,6,F"He lives and breathes the Customs
OL,7,FHouse, it's such a special place to
OL,8,Fhim," said Joe. "I think he cares
OL,9,Fabout it the way the community cares
OL,10,Fabout this venue.
OL,12,F"The last few years certainly
OL,13,Fthroughout the pandemic when times
OL,14,Fwere very uncertain, he was pushing
OL,15,Fand making things happen at the
OL,16,FCustoms House."
